God!  What have I done?  It must have been the fermented peaches on the pound cake.<br>
Good thing for me...I live on the prairie.. I can see for miles in any direction.  Been glassing the horizon for a white comode seat being bourne along by a bright blue and red conveyance with yellow pin striping.<br>
I've got donuts hanging in the wire.  That ought to slow him down... air bourne lawnmower is in the launch mode.<br>
On the other hand...Marines have a short memory span.  He might forget why he came here.  Better check my stash of trading material.  I've got a couple cans of spam.. two cross bows.. a picture of John Wayne.. and some used motorcycle tires... that ought to work.<br>
I could plead insanity or PTSD.<br>
Had a bit of panic... thought he was coming.. but it was just a red and blue RC Cola can.. Can't trust these Wal Mart binoculars!<br>
Its the silence before the battle that kills you!<br><br>
